00:17:21,520 --> 00:17:24,700
Why do you call that stinker "Young Cabinet Master"?

255
00:17:24,700 --> 00:17:27,070
Qin Huaizhang and Long Que were close friends in life and death.

256
00:17:27,070 --> 00:17:30,020
