325
00:21:24,260 --> 00:21:27,270
Sixteen disciples of the Iron Fist Gang died in an inn,

326
00:21:27,270 --> 00:21:30,090
one word carved on each of their chests,

327
00:21:30,090 --> 00:21:32,300
