00:23:33,980 --> 00:23:37,690
[Giant Whale Gang]

355
00:23:38,650 --> 00:23:40,250
This infuriates me!

356
00:23:40,250 --> 00:23:44,190
Leader, you should reconsider leaving the Five Lakes Alliance.

357
00:23:44,190 --> 00:23:46,380
Reconsider, my ass!

