00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:33,230
Four Great Assassins, Venomous Scorpions?

368
00:24:35,700 --> 00:24:40,460
Alliance Leader Zhao, the rumors are not false.

369
00:24:40,460 --> 00:24:44,750
